+Sem/Cat         !!≈ * @CODE@ = Category
+Sem/Clth        !!≈ * @CODE@ = Clothes
+Sem/Clth-jewl   !!≈ * @CODE@ = Jewelery
+Sem/Clthpart    !!≈ * @CODE@ = part of clothes
+Sem/Ctain       !!≈ * @CODE@ = Container
