+Sem/Food-med    !!≈ * @CODE@ = Medicine
+Sem/Fruit       !!≈ * @CODE@ = Fruits, vegetables, seeds, nuts
+Sem/Furn        !!≈ * @CODE@ = Furniture
+Sem/Game        !!≈ * @CODE@ = Game
+Sem/Geom        !!≈ * @CODE@ = Geometrical object
